description:
After the surprising arrival of a new Angeloid named Nymph, the gang heads to the beach! Nymph seems to have a bit of an attitude, but she’s still willing to help when Sohara’s lack of swimming skills puts her in a serious situation.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Swimsuit Surf Brigade, Go! Go! Go!
